hadiths[40]{hadithnumber,text}:
3969,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (Sura Baqara ki aayat (125) yun) qirat farmaee : (وَاتَّخِذُوا مِنْ مَقَامِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ مُصَلًّى) (''خا'' ke nichey zer ke sath ba-seegha Amr padha) aur maqame Ibrahim ko jaey-Namaz bana lo.
3970,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke eik shakhs ne raat ko qiyam kiya aur qirate-Quran main apni aawaz buland ki. subh hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah falan par rehem farmaai ! usney aaj raat mujhey kitni hi aayaat yaad dila den jin se mujhey zahul ho raha tha.''
3971,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke aayat kareema (وَمَا كَانَ لِنَبِيٍّ أَنْ يَغُلَّ . . ۔) aakhir tak is silsiley mein nazil hui thi ke Badr ke din eik surkh rang ka kapda gum ho gaya tha to kaee logon ne keh diya ke shayad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ley liya ho. to Shan Wale Allah ne ye aayat nazil farmaey ( وَمَا كَانَ لِنَبِيٍّ أَنْ يَغُلَّ . . ۔) aakhir tak ''ye na-mumkin hai ke koi Nabi khayanat karey, aur jo koi khayanat kerega to jo usney khayanat ki hogi uskey sath qiyamat ke din hazir hoga, phir her shakhs ko pura pura badla diya jaeyga aur un par zulm nahin kiya jaeyga.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke lafz (يغل) ''ya'' par zabar ke sath hai."
3972,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (eik dua mein) farmaya : (اللهم! إني أعوذ بك من البخل والهرم) ''aey Allah ! main bakheeli aur aajiz kar deney waley budhapey se teri panah chahta hun.''
3973,"Hazrat Laqeet bin Sabra (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke bani Muntafiq ka wafad jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya tha main us mein shareek tha. . . aur hadees bayan ki . . . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye mat samajhna'' (ke ye bakri ham ne tumhari khatir zibeh ki hai) aur hadees bayan ki. aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (لَا تَحْسِبَنَّ) ( ''seen'' ki zer sey) farmaya , (zabar ke sath) ( لَا تَحْسَبَنَّ ( nahin farmaya tha.''"
3974,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi apni chand bakriyan liye ja raha tha ke musalman us par ja pahunchey to usney kaha : ''السلام علیکم.'' magar musalmanon ne usey qatl kar diya aur un chand bakriyon par qabza kar liya. to is par ye aayat kareema nazil hui (وَلَا تَقُولُوا لِمَنْ أَلْقَى إِلَيْكُمْ السَّلَامَ لَسْتَ مُؤْمِنًا تَبْتَغُونَ عَرَضَ الْحَيَاةِ الدُّنْيَا) '' aur jo shakhs tumhen salam kahey uskey baarey mein ye mat kaho ke to sahibe emaan nahin hai. tum duniya ki zindagaani ke maal ke mutalaashi (khoji) ho?'' is aayat mein unhi chand bakriyon ki taraf ishara hai.
3975,Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye aayat yun padha kartey they (لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين غير أولي الضرر) '' momineen mein se ( jihad sey) beth rehney waley is haal mein ke unhen koi uzr ho aur jihad par janey waley barabar nahin ho saktey .''
3976,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yun qirat ki) وَالْعَيْنُ بِالْعَيْنِ ( ) pesh ke sath ( yani sura maayda ki aayat : 45 mein) وَكَتَبْنَا عَلَيْهِمْ فِيهَا أَنَّ النَّفْسَ بِالنَّفْسِ وَالْعَيْنُ بِالْعَيْنِ . . . الخ ( padha .
3977,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qirat farmaai : ( وَكَتَبْنَا عَلَيْهِمْ فِيهَا أَنَّ النَّفْسَ بِالنَّفْسِ وَالْعَيْنُ بِالْعَيْنِ ( (yani ( un ( ko mukhaffaf aur) العین ( ko marfoo padha .)
3978,Atiya bin Saad Aufi kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) par qirat ki aur yun padha ( اللَّهُ الَّذِي خَلَقَكُمْ مِنْ ضَعْفٍ ( ) ضاد par فتحہ ke sath ( to unhoney farmaya : ( مِنْ ضُعْفٍ ( padho . (yani ضاد par ضمہ hai) maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par ye aayat isi tarah padhi thi jaisey ke tune mujh par padhi hai to aapney meri giraft farmaai jaisey ke maine tumhari giraft ki hai.
3979,Janab Atiya ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ( مِنْ ضُعْفٍ ( naqal kya hai. (yani ضاد par ضمہ ke sath .)
3980,Abdur-Rehman bin Abza ki riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ( بِفَضْلِ اللَّهِ وَبِرَحْمَتِهِ فَبِذَلِكَ فَلْتَفْرَحُوا ( yani khitab kartey huey. jabkey hamari maroof qirat ghayeb key taur par) فَلْیَفْرَحُوا ( hai.'' keh diijiye ke Allah ka fazal aur uski meharbani hai. chunanche usi par tumhen / unhen khush hona chahiye .''
3981,Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qirat farmaai : ( بِفَضْلِ اللَّهِ وَبِرَحْمَتِهِ فَبِذَلِكَ فَلْتَفْرَحُوا هُوَ خَيْرٌ مِمَّا تَجْمَعُونَ ( yani ( فلتفرحوا ( . . . aur . . .) تجمعون ( . . . dono khitab ke taur par padhey. jabkey Hafs ki qirat mein ghaib ke taur par) فليفرحوا (aur ( یجمعون ( hai.
3982,Hazrat Asma binte-Yazeed (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko qirat kartey huey suna : (إِنَّهُ عَمِلَ غَيْرَ صَالِحٍ) yani ( عَمِل ( فعل maazi aur) غَيْرَ ( مفعول bih yani mansoob .
3983,Janab shehar bin Hoshab kehtey hain ke maine umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye aayat kis tarah padha kartey they : (إِنَّهُ عَمِلَ غَيْرَ صَالِحٍ) to unhoney farmaya : aapney usko (إِنَّهُ عَمِلَ غَيْرَ صَالِحٍ) padha tha. (yani maazi ke taur par) . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain us riwayat ko Harun Nahwi aur Musa bin khalaf ne Sabit ( Sabit Bunani ( se usi tarah riwayat kya hai jaisey ke Abdul-Azeez ne kaha hai.
3984,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se naqal kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab dua farmatey to pehley apney aap se ibtida (shuruat) farmatey aur kehtey : (رحمة الله علينا وعلى موسى) ''Allah ki rehmat ho ham par aur Musa par . agar wo sabr kar letey to wo apney sahab ( khizr ( se bahut Ajaaib dekhtey , lekin unhoney khud hi keh diya : agar uskey baad mein aap se koi sawal karun to aap mujhey apney sath mat rakhen . aap meri taraf se mazrat ko pahunch chukey .'' (Hamza Zayyat ne lafz ( لدني ( ko tool de-kar yani daal ke pesh aur noon ki shad ke sath bhari karkey padha .) ye mazmoon sura kahaf , aayat : 76 ka hai. ("
3985,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya ke aapney ( قَدْ بَلَغْتَ مِنْ لَدُنِّي ( ki qirat mein) لدني ( ko ثقیل karkey padha ( shad ke sath ("
3986,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey they ke Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey usi tarah padhaya jaisey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen padhaya tha yani ( فِي عَيْنٍ حَمِئَةٍ )
3987,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jannat ke aa'la darjaat ke hamil ehle illiyeen ka eik shakhs ooper se jannatiyon par jhaankey ga to jannat uskey chehrey se damak uthegi goya koi chamakta damakta sitaara ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke hadees ki riwayat aisey hi hai. aur abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) yaqinan unhi mein se hain aur badi fazilat waley hain.
3988,"Hazrat Farwa bin Musaik Ghatifi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua , aur hadees bayan ki . qom mein se eik shakhs ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap hamen bataeyn ke saba ilaqey ka naam hai ya aurat ka ? aapney farmaya : ''ye ilaqey ka naam hai na kisi aurat ka , balke arab ka aadmi tha jiskey das bete they jin mein se chhe Yamen chaley gaey they aur chaar ne shaam mein sukunat ikhtiyar kar li thi.'' Usman bin abi Sheba ne Ghatifi ki bajaey ghatfaani kaha aur sanad mein حدثنا الحسن بن الحكم النخعي kaha ."
3989,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se wahi wali hadees bayan ki aur kaha ke usi silsiley mein Allah ka ye farman hai) حَتَّى إِذَا فُزِّعَ عَنْ قُلُوبِهِمْ ( '' yahan tak ke jab un farishton ke dilon se ghabrahat door ki jati hai.''
3990,"ummul-momenin Sayeda umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai, wo farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat thi ( بَلَى قَدْ جَاءَتْكِ آيَاتِي فَكَذَبْتِ بِهَا وَاسْتَكْبَرْتِ وَكُنْتِ مِنْ الْكَافِرِينَ ( ) الزمر : 59 ( (yani wahid muannas mukhatib ke Seeghon mein '' kaaf '' aur '' taa '' ke kasara ke sath. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ye hadees mursal hai. Rabeea (bin Anas ( ne Sayeda umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ko nahin paya ."
3991,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko padhtey huey suna ( فَرُوحٌ وَرَيْحَانٌ ( ) الواقعۃ : 89 ( (yani lafz rooh mein '' raa '' ke ضمہ ke sath .)
3992,Janab Safwan bin Yaala apney walid Yaala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna . aap member par khadey padh rahey they ( وَنَادَوْا يَا مَالِكُ ( '' jahannami pukarengey aey malik! (darogha jahannam).
3993,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey padhaya hai) إِنِّي أَنَا الرَّزَّاقُ ذُو الْقُوَّةِ الْمَتِينُ ( ''bila-shuba main hi rizq deney wala, quwat wala aur zor aawar hun.''"
3994,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) padha kartey they : ( فَهَلْ مِنْ مُدَّكِرٍ ( yani shad ke sath .'' bhala koi hai jo nasihat pakdey . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye lafz '' meem '' ke ضمہ '' , daal '' ke فتحہ aur '' kaaf '' ke kasaraa ke sath hai."
3995,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha aap padh rahey they : ( أَ يَحْسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُ أَخْلَدَهُ ( ) الھمزۃ : 3 ( (yani shuru mein Hamza istefhaam ke sath .)
3996,"Janab abu-Qulaba us shakhs se riwayat kartey hain jis ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne padhaya tha : ( فَيَوْمَئِذٍ لَا يُعَذَّبُ عَذَابَهُ أَحَدٌ وَلَا يُوثَقُ وَثَاقَهُ أَحَدٌ ( ) الفجر : 25 , 26 ( yani ( يعذب (aur ( يوثق ( majhool Seeghon ke sath . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke baaz raawiyon ne Khalid aur abu-Qulaba ke darmiyan eik raawi ka izafa kya hai."
3997,"Janab Abu-Qulaba kehtey hain ke mujhey us shakhs ne bataya jis ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne padhaya tha. ya kaha . . . mujhey us shakhs ne padhaya jis ko us shakhs ne padhaya jisey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne padhaya tha (فَيَوْمَئِذٍ لَا يُعَذَّبُ) (''zaal'') ke zabar, yani majhool seedhey ke sath.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Aasim , Aamash , Talha bin Musrif , Abu-Jaafar Yazid bin Qaaqaa , Sheba bin Nasaah . Naafe bin Abdur-Rehman , Abdullah bin Kaseer Daari , Abu-Amr bin Al Ulaa , Hamza Zayyaat , Abdur-Rehman Aaraj , Qatada , Hasan Basri , Mujahid , Humaid Aaraj , Abdullah bin Abbas aur Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Bakar ye sabhi hazraat (لَا يُعَذِّبُ وَلَا يُوثِقُ‏) padhtey hain (''zaal'' aur ''ثا'' ke kasaraa , yani maroof seedhey ke sath).  magar marfoo hadees mein) يُعَذَّبُ ( ''zaal'' ke فتحہ ke sath marwi (bayan) hai."
3998,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik hadees bayan farmaee. is mein Jibrael aur Meekaal ka zikr tha to aapney (unke talaffuz mein) ''(Jibraaeel) aur (Meekaail) farmaya.''
3999,"Muhammad bin Khazim ne bayan kiya ke Janab Aamash ki majlis mein (Jibraaeel) aur (Meekaail) ke talaffuz ki behes chal padi to Aamash ne ba-sand Saad Taai , Atiya Aufi se unhoney Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sur phoonkney waley farishtey (Israafeel) ka zikr kiya aur farmaya : ''uski daain janib ''Jibraaeel'' aur uski baeyn janib ''Meekaail'' hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya ke (Khalaf) kehtey hain : chaalis saal honey ko aaye hain ke maine likhney se qalam nahin uthaya hai magar mujhey jo uljhan ''Jibrael aur Meekaail'' ke zabt mein hui hai kisi aur kaime mein nahin hui."
4000,"Janab Zohri (Rahimahullah) baaz-oqaat ibne Musaiyab se riwayat kartey they, unhoney kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , Abu-Bakar , umr aur Usman (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) (مَالِكِ يَوْمِ الدِّينِ) padha kartey they (Sura Fatiha mein , (ملك)  بروزن فاعل .) aur Marwan sab se pehla shakhs hai jisney ye (مَلِكِ يَوْمِ الدِّينِ) padha. (''الف'' ke baghair بروزن فاعل). Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye sanad Zohri (an) Anas aur Zohri (an) Salim (an) Abih ki ba-nisbat ziyada sahih hai."
4001,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat ka zikr kiya (بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ مَلِكِ يَوْمِ الدِّينِ) aap apni qirat main eik eik lafz alehda alehda karkey padhtey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain maine Imam Ahmed (Rahimahullah) se suna, wo farmatey they : qadim qirat (Salaf ki qirat) (مالك يوم الدين) hi hai."
4002,Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath sawari par peechhey baitha hua tha jabkey aap gadhey par Sawar they aur Suraj ghuroob honey wala tha. aapney farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ke ye kahan ghuroob hota hai? ''maine kaha : Allah aur uska Rasool hi behtar jantey hain. aapney farmaya : (فَإِنَّهَا تَغْرُبُ فِي عَيْنٍ حَامِيَةٍ) ''ye eik garm chashmey mein ghuroob hota hai.''
4003,"Hazrat Waasila bin Isqaa' (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke paas aaye aur chabootrey par tashrif laye jo muhajrin ke liye makhsus tha, to eik aadmi ne aap se puchha ke Quran karim ki kon si aayat sab se badi hai? aapney farmaya : (الله لا إله إلا هو الحى القيوم لا تأخذه سنة ولا نوم) (yani Aayatal Kursi)."
4004,Janab Shaqiq se riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne padha : (هَيْتَ لَكَ) (''ھا'' par zabar ke sath) Shaqiq ke kaha ham usey (هِئْتُ لَكَ) padhtey hain (yani ''ھا'' ke nichey zer ke sath) to ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jaisey mujhey padhaya gaya usi tarah padhna mujhey ziyada mehboob hai.
4005,Janab Shaqiq se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha gaya ke log ye aayat kareema (وَقَالَتْ هِيتَ لَكَ) padhtey hain (yani ''ھا'' ke zer ke sath) to unhoney kaha : bila-shuba mujhey usi tarah padhna ziyada mehboob hai jaisey ke mujhey sikhaya gaya hai (وَقَالَتْ هَيْتَ لَكَ) (yani ''ھا'' par zabar ke sath).
4006,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Shan Wale Allah ne bani-Israel se farmaya : ({ادْخُلُوا الْبَابَ سُجَّدًا وَقُولُوا حِطَّةٌ تُغْفَرْ لَكُمْ خَطَايَاكُمْ}) (البقرۃ : 58) yani (تغفر) ''taa'' ke ضمہ se b-seegha wahid muannas ghayeb majhool."
4007,"Jaafar bin Musafir ne ibne-Abi Fidyak sey, unhoney Hisham bin Saad sey, unhoney apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ki misl (jaisi) riwayat kiya."
4008,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par wahi nazil hui to aapney hamen ye aayaat padh kar sunaee (سُورَةٌ أَنْزَلْنَاهَا وَفَرَضْنَاهَا). Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke aapney (فرضناها) ka kalma ''raa'' ki) kami se padha yahan tak ke un aayaat par pahunchey (jin mein Sayeda Aaisha Tayiba ko un par lage ilzaam se bari kar diya gaya hai).
